                         resolution="72"/>
            </figure>
            <para>Effective April 1998 Hendrickson will replace suspension springs in production for the
                RT2/RTE2-400/460/480 and RT2-520 with the springs listed in the matrix below. The discontinued springs
                are obsolete and will no longer be available. Also effective April 1998, the Number 1 and 2 leaves will
                no longer be available for service on spring assembly part numbers 58179, 58252, 58847, 58195, and
                58251. It is recommended that the complete spring assembly be replaced as listed below.
            </para>
            <para>The current springs maintain a higher level of performance in durability and handling in severe
                applications. The current springs are completely interchangeable with the discontinued springs. For more
                information, contact your local Hendrickson parts supplier, truck dealer or call Hendrickson Tech
                Services at 630-910-2800.
            </para>
